WEBVTT

00:04:27.508 --> 00:04:32.938
(Applause)

00:04:33.080 --> 00:04:34.416
So you are scared of exams,

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:35.440
yes, I got that!

00:04:35.440 --> 00:04:37.280
(Laughter)

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:40.136
I have been saying this
all over the world,

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:43.360
nobody has done it yet,
but they will do it.

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:47.896
Now what will happen
in "school in the cloud?"

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:48.927
You will not teach.

00:04:48.927 --> 00:04:52.096
If you want to teach about volcanoes,
you will go to class and say,

00:04:52.096 --> 00:04:55.816
“I had planned to teach
about volcanoes today

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:58.416
but I will not teach.

00:04:58.440 --> 00:05:02.280
I will give you twenty minutes,
then you tell me.”